<p>ATC代碼第一級不使用 <span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">E</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">F</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">I</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">K</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">O</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">Q</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">T</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">U</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">W</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">X</span></span>，<span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">Y</span></span> 和 <span title="英語文本"><span lang="en">Z</span></span> 字母。
